# The Ramayana in Sanskrit

------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a version of the Ramayana in Sanskrit derived from files created
by Prof. Muneo Tokunaga of Kyoto and edited by John D. Smith. This has
parallel Devanagari and Romanization. We have not attempted to
cross-reference this yet with the [Griffith translation](../rama/index.md),
due to the mismatch in number of chapters per book.

**IMPORTANT NOTE**: This etext uses Unicode extensively. You will need
to make sure that your browser is set up to view Unicode properly. For
more information, read the [Unicode page](../../unicode.md).

